♪The distant land might be dangerous♪

18
00:01:24,180 --> 00:01:27,020
♪But what's life without an adventure?♪

19
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:30,100
♪Youths are supposed to dream big and be sharp♪

20
00:01:30,340 --> 00:01:33,420
♪Every struggle in life has taught us♪

21
00:01:33,420 --> 00:01:35,380
♪That we shall do what we can wherever we go♪

22
00:01:35,380 --> 00:01:40,900
♪Together, another journey awaits♪

23
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:50,020
[The Blood of Youth]

24
00:01:50,250 --> 00:01:52,970
[Episode 15]

25
00:01:56,300 --> 00:01:56,820
Your Highness,

26
00:01:57,660 --> 00:01:59,100
I thought we would be able

27
00:01:59,580 --> 00:02:00,260
to see those

28
00:02:00,260 --> 00:02:01,700
cunning old fellows in Wushuang City.

29
00:02:02,260 --> 00:02:02,940
I never expected

30
00:02:02,940 --> 00:02:03,700
to see a city lord

31
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:04,580
as young as him.

32
00:02:06,180 --> 00:02:07,700
This new city lord

33
00:02:07,740 --> 00:02:08,580
with a bad memory

34
00:02:10,060 --> 00:02:11,300
is much harder to deal with

35
00:02:11,300 --> 00:02:12,180
than those five old guys.

36
00:02:12,700 --> 00:02:13,660
Your Highness, was that why

37
00:02:13,860 --> 00:02:14,540
you didn't involve them

38
00:02:14,700 --> 00:02:15,460
in our plan?

39
00:02:15,860 --> 00:02:16,580
That's right.

40
00:02:17,620 --> 00:02:18,420
When we play weiqi,

41
00:02:19,500 --> 00:02:20,620
we need to have room for maneuver.

42
00:02:21,620 --> 00:02:22,540
Wushuang City

43
00:02:23,460 --> 00:02:24,420
is the maneuver.

44
00:02:25,460 --> 00:02:26,060
If so, Your Highness,

45
00:02:26,860 --> 00:02:28,100
where are we heading next?

46
00:02:28,700 --> 00:02:29,620
We'll go meet Jingxia.

47
00:02:30,220 --> 00:02:31,580
He said he has something important
to discuss with me.

48
00:02:32,410 --> 00:02:33,820
The Ninth Prince?

49
00:02:34,300 --> 00:02:35,380
The Ninth Prince is...

50
00:02:35,740 --> 00:02:37,140
What are you mumbling about?

51
00:02:38,660 --> 00:02:39,580
The Ninth Prince is...

52
00:02:39,940 --> 00:02:40,700
What's wrong with Jingxia?

53
00:02:41,340 --> 00:02:42,300
He went looking for the Dark River.

54
00:02:42,820 --> 00:02:43,500
What?

55
00:02:58,460 --> 00:02:58,900
Who's there?

56
00:02:59,980 --> 00:03:01,380
Leader sent me here to receive you.

57
00:03:02,340 --> 00:03:03,820
[Xiao Jingxia, Ninth Prince]

58
00:03:06,340 --> 00:03:07,060
Leader

59
00:03:08,220 --> 00:03:09,060
knows that I'm coming?

60
00:03:14,540 --> 00:03:15,260
I heard from people

61
00:03:16,020 --> 00:03:16,980
that there's a river

62
00:03:16,980 --> 00:03:17,780
that cannot be seen.

63
00:03:18,740 --> 00:03:19,900
You can only barely see it

64
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:21,020
on the darkest of nights

65
00:03:21,020 --> 00:03:22,140
following the moonlight.

66
00:03:23,220 --> 00:03:24,580
If I follow the river,

67
00:03:26,020 --> 00:03:27,460
I can find Dark River, the number one assassin

68
00:03:27,860 --> 00:03:28,980
in the League of Assassins.

69
00:03:29,580 --> 00:03:30,660
I never expected it to be true.

70
00:03:34,380 --> 00:03:35,300
There are three families in Dark River.

71
00:03:36,100 --> 00:03:37,540
Su family, the weapon experts,

72
00:03:37,940 --> 00:03:39,380
Xie family, the internal energy fist experts,

73
00:03:39,940 --> 00:03:41,340
and Mu family, the medical experts.

74
00:03:42,180 --> 00:03:43,860
The three families have control
over their top martial arts experts.

75
00:03:44,340 --> 00:03:45,340
And the Leader is their head.

76
00:03:45,900 --> 00:03:48,180
You must be the head of the Su family.

77
00:03:48,980 --> 00:03:49,940
[Su Muyu, Dark River]
Su Muyu.

78
00:03:51,020 --> 00:03:52,580
That's right. Su Muyu is the name.

79
00:03:53,580 --> 00:03:54,340
I even heard

80
00:03:55,260 --> 00:03:55,940
that your name

81
00:03:55,940 --> 00:03:57,020
is related to your umbrella.

82
00:03:58,500 --> 00:03:59,300
Within your umbrella,

83
00:03:59,300 --> 00:04:00,180
there contains 18 longswords.

84
00:04:01,220 --> 00:04:02,180
When you release your killing intent,

85
00:04:02,620 --> 00:04:03,580
18 of them

86
00:04:03,580 --> 00:04:04,420
will be discharged from your umbrella,

87
00:04:05,180 --> 00:04:06,020
just like the evening rain.

88
00:04:11,220 --> 00:04:12,140
You know us well.

89
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:15,220
Of course,

90
00:04:16,020 --> 00:04:17,420
since I need to do business with you all.

91
00:04:17,860 --> 00:04:18,660
Knowing us too well

92
00:04:18,980 --> 00:04:20,300
is a dangerous thing.

93
00:04:34,780 --> 00:04:36,300
Leader, I've brought him here.

94
00:04:42,460 --> 00:04:43,220
Greetings, Leader.

95
00:04:45,260 --> 00:04:46,860
Greetings, Xie Qidao, Head of the Xie family.

96
00:04:46,860 --> 00:04:47,260
[Xie Qidao, Dark River]

97
00:04:48,660 --> 00:04:50,900
Greetings, Mu Yumo, Head of the Mu family.

98
00:04:53,380 --> 00:04:56,940
Seems like you know us very well.

99
00:04:58,660 --> 00:05:00,140
No one dares to step into

100
00:05:01,180 --> 00:05:02,740
the Falling Stars Pavilion

101
00:05:03,180 --> 00:05:04,140
and do business with the Dark River

102
00:05:04,620 --> 00:05:05,820
without any knowledge of you all.

103
00:05:07,100 --> 00:05:08,220
Since you know who we are,

104
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:11,060
[Mu Yumo, Dark River]
you should know that doing business with us

105
00:05:11,780 --> 00:05:13,100
is very dangerous.

106
00:05:13,900 --> 00:05:14,940
The riskier

107
00:05:15,900 --> 00:05:16,700
certain things are,

108
00:05:17,460 --> 00:05:18,580
the more meaningful they are, am I right?

109
00:05:19,140 --> 00:05:20,180
You're right.

110
00:05:23,820 --> 00:05:26,500
[Su Changhe, Dark River]

111
00:05:30,940 --> 00:05:31,580
So,

112
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:34,740
what kind of meaningful event

113
00:05:35,700 --> 00:05:37,580
have you brought to us today?

114
00:05:40,500 --> 00:05:41,340
I want

115
00:05:41,340 --> 00:05:42,340
the Dark River

116
00:05:44,220 --> 00:05:45,220
to move to Tianqi.

117
00:05:47,380 --> 00:05:48,860
[To Su Changhe: I, Xiao, would like to
invite everyone to join hands with the Tang Clan]

118
00:05:48,860 --> 00:05:50,140
[and eradicate the Lei Clan.
Xiao Chuhe will reward you all greatly.]

119
00:05:54,260 --> 00:05:54,860
Muyu,

120
00:05:56,740 --> 00:05:57,500
how long has it been

121
00:05:57,660 --> 00:05:58,820
since you last

122
00:05:59,580 --> 00:06:00,860
fought together with her?

123
00:06:01,580 --> 00:06:02,660
It's been more than 12 years.

124
00:06:04,220 --> 00:06:05,340
Now that you're venturing
into the martial arts world again,

125
00:06:06,180 --> 00:06:08,540
you and she will be enemies.

126
00:06:09,260 --> 00:06:11,820
I'm sure you're not willing to do it.

127
00:06:12,820 --> 00:06:13,740
I don't agree with dragging

128
00:06:13,780 --> 00:06:14,700
Dark River into such matters.

129
00:06:15,020 --> 00:06:17,020
However, I know you have your reasons.

130
00:06:18,060 --> 00:06:18,940
I'm a member of the Su family.

131
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:20,660
So I will follow

132
00:06:20,660 --> 00:06:21,540
the Leader's order.

133
00:06:25,260 --> 00:06:26,500
I've always been looking for

134
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:28,180
the shore on the other side.

135
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:30,300
I hope that we can

136
00:06:31,100 --> 00:06:32,250
clear our identities as assassins

137
00:06:32,250 --> 00:06:33,820
after getting ashore

138
00:06:34,460 --> 00:06:36,340
and be above board once again.

139
00:06:37,060 --> 00:06:37,980
And this event

140
00:06:39,140 --> 00:06:40,820
will be our best chance

141
00:06:40,820 --> 00:06:41,860
at redeeming ourselves.

142
00:06:43,940 --> 00:06:45,060
However, many people will die.

143
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:47,900
Death

144
00:06:49,140 --> 00:06:50,220
is the most common thing

145
00:06:51,340 --> 00:06:52,380
within Dark River.

146
00:06:54,420 --> 00:06:55,100
Although

147
00:06:55,940 --> 00:06:57,620
you've already stated your identity
in the letter,

148
00:06:58,020 --> 00:06:59,140
I wish to listen

149
00:06:59,300 --> 00:07:00,300
to your introduction

150
00:07:01,420 --> 00:07:02,620
personally.

151
00:07:06,100 --> 00:07:08,100
I'm the Sixth Prince of the Beili Kingdom,

152
00:07:08,980 --> 00:07:11,020
Xiao Chuhe.

153
00:07:16,620 --> 00:07:17,340
I'm Lei Wujie from the Lei family

154
00:07:17,820 --> 00:07:18,580
of Jiangnan Thunderbolt Sect.

155
00:07:19,260 --> 00:07:20,100
I'm here to pay a visit.

156
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:23,020
I cannot hear you.

157
00:07:26,660 --> 00:07:28,060
This is how you challenge Mount Wangcheng?

158
00:07:28,300 --> 00:07:29,140
You should raise your voice.

159
00:07:30,980 --> 00:07:33,060
It's our first time here.

160
00:07:33,260 --> 00:07:35,100
Shouldn't we act courteously?

161
00:07:35,300 --> 00:07:36,700
They didn't invite you to be their guest.

162
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:38,140
You're a disciple of Xueyue City

163
00:07:38,300 --> 00:07:39,340
and the younger brother of a sword deity.

164
00:07:40,100 --> 00:07:40,900
You should be imposing.

165
00:07:41,740 --> 00:07:42,380
That's right.

166
00:07:43,060 --> 00:07:44,100
I'm the disciple of Xueyue City

167
00:07:44,460 --> 00:07:45,340
and the younger brother of a sword deity.

168
00:07:46,460 --> 00:07:47,620
I've seen the elephant.

169
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:50,460
What are you guys doing?

170
00:07:50,700 --> 00:07:52,460
[Be Open-Minded]

171
00:07:58,180 --> 00:07:58,860
The Tingyu Sword?

172
00:07:59,700 --> 00:08:00,620
I'm Lei Wujie from the Lei family

173
00:08:01,180 --> 00:08:03,580
of Jiangnan Thunderbolt Sect, here to...

174
00:08:08,060 --> 00:08:08,780
What are you doing here?

175
00:08:09,260 --> 00:08:10,380
I was just imitating you

176
00:08:10,460 --> 00:08:11,380
in challenging Mount Wangcheng.

177
00:08:11,860 --> 00:08:13,180
Are you trying to kill me here?

178
00:08:17,060 --> 00:08:17,660
Who's there?

179
00:08:19,180 --> 00:08:20,020
-Master.
-Grand Martial Uncle.

180
00:08:21,980 --> 00:08:23,060
So, you're Zhao Yuzhen?

181
00:08:24,100 --> 00:08:24,700
Tingyu?

182
00:08:27,860 --> 00:08:28,700
How did that happen?

183
00:08:30,700 --> 00:08:31,300
I felt

184
00:08:31,420 --> 00:08:32,460
Tingyu's sword intent just now.

185
00:08:33,340 --> 00:08:34,380
I thought she was here.

186
00:08:37,860 --> 00:08:38,380
Who are you?

187
00:08:39,140 --> 00:08:39,980
Since you don't know who I am,

188
00:08:40,660 --> 00:08:42,100
I'll beat my name into your head.

189
00:08:43,260 --> 00:08:43,820
He must be out of his mind.

190
00:08:50,860 --> 00:08:51,340
Repel Thunder.

191
00:08:53,580 --> 00:08:54,300
Judging from your technique,

192
00:08:54,740 --> 00:08:56,300
you must come from the same sect
as the one who rides a crane.

193
00:08:57,220 --> 00:08:57,860
The Lei family

194
00:08:57,860 --> 00:08:58,700
is truly interesting.

195
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:00,340
Why do you always want to come to

196
00:09:00,340 --> 00:09:00,980
Mount Wangcheng?

197
00:09:01,980 --> 00:09:03,380
Try this technique for size.

198
00:09:03,980 --> 00:09:06,460
I inherited this sword art from a sword deity.
It's called Beautiful Day.

199
00:09:32,500 --> 00:09:33,700
Zhao Yuzhen is protected by zhenqi.

200
00:09:34,100 --> 00:09:35,020
You won't be able to harm him

201
00:09:35,100 --> 00:09:35,940
no matter what you do.

202
00:09:38,220 --> 00:09:39,340
You're her disciple indeed.

203
00:09:42,620 --> 00:09:43,500
Did she tell you to come see me?

204
00:09:44,180 --> 00:09:44,820
How is she doing?

205
00:09:45,420 --> 00:09:46,140
I was just trying to vent my sister's anger

206
00:09:46,300 --> 00:09:46,940
on her behalf.

207
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:48,140
You're her younger brother?

208
00:09:48,900 --> 00:09:49,700
You have so many questions.

209
00:09:49,900 --> 00:09:51,340
Why don't you ask her yourself?

210
00:09:53,660 --> 00:09:54,140
She said

211
00:09:55,260 --> 00:09:56,420
she wanted me to follow her down the mountain

212
00:09:57,100 --> 00:09:57,980
after her third visit.

213
00:09:58,820 --> 00:09:59,740
I've been waiting for her for many years.

214
00:10:00,340 --> 00:10:01,340
But she never came.

215
00:10:02,300 --> 00:10:03,180
She came.

216
00:10:03,820 --> 00:10:04,580
She did?

217
00:10:05,420 --> 00:10:06,100
That's impossible.

218
00:10:06,580 --> 00:10:07,740
I know everything there is to know

219
00:10:07,740 --> 00:10:08,700
on this mountain.

220
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:10,580
I'd have known if she had been here.

221
00:10:13,460 --> 00:10:14,820
Back then, you were cultivating in seclusion.

222
00:10:15,500 --> 00:10:16,460
After that, Lei Yunhe came here

223
00:10:17,500 --> 00:10:18,420
to challenge you.

224
00:10:30,340 --> 00:10:32,180
(You broke one of his arms and chased him off.)

225
00:10:32,820 --> 00:10:34,220
(However, you were seriously wounded too.)

226
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:35,820
(You almost went berserk.)

227
00:10:36,980 --> 00:10:38,740
You rested and recuperated

228
00:10:39,740 --> 00:10:40,700
with the support of all celestial masters.

229
00:10:41,420 --> 00:10:42,340
(During that period,)

230
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:44,300
(Li Hanyi did come.)

231
00:10:45,420 --> 00:10:46,060
(The entire Mount Wangcheng)

232
00:10:46,060 --> 00:10:47,460
(should know about it.)

233
00:10:54,060 --> 00:10:57,300
[Mount Wangcheng]

234
00:11:05,580 --> 00:11:06,100
But...

235
00:11:07,460 --> 00:11:08,300
I truly have no idea.

236
00:11:11,540 --> 00:11:12,220
Master,

237
00:11:12,500 --> 00:11:14,620
back then, I wasn't your disciple yet.

238
00:11:15,300 --> 00:11:16,340
Grand Martial Uncle, back then,

239
00:11:16,580 --> 00:11:17,340
I wasn't born yet.

240
00:11:18,460 --> 00:11:19,100
Yuzhen.

241
00:11:20,180 --> 00:11:20,740
Martial Uncle Yin.

242
00:11:21,580 --> 00:11:21,980
Martial Uncle Yin,

243
00:11:21,980 --> 00:11:22,780
what exactly is going on?

244
00:11:24,340 --> 00:11:25,060
Do you remember

245
00:11:25,500 --> 00:11:26,980
the last day of your master's

246
00:11:26,980 --> 00:11:27,860
cultivation in seclusion?

247
00:11:30,340 --> 00:11:30,980
Yuzhen,

248
00:11:31,620 --> 00:11:33,460
you cannot leave the mountain.

249
00:11:33,980 --> 00:11:36,580
I've predicted your destiny.

250
00:11:38,100 --> 00:11:39,820
Master, I've never doubted your words.

251
00:11:40,500 --> 00:11:42,580
No one has ever won against the heavens.

252
00:11:42,940 --> 00:11:44,420
However, I wish to try

253
00:11:45,180 --> 00:11:47,340
and see if I can deceive the heavens.

254
00:11:48,020 --> 00:11:48,740
How?

255
00:11:51,060 --> 00:11:53,020
Try to reach the Unbeatable Phase.

256
00:11:53,500 --> 00:11:54,220
The Unbeatable Phase?

257
00:11:54,820 --> 00:11:55,820
Once you do so,

258
00:11:56,020 --> 00:11:56,980
even the heavens

259
00:11:57,220 --> 00:11:58,460
can no longer restrict you.

260
00:11:59,260 --> 00:12:01,100
In order to help you achieve that phase,

261
00:12:01,820 --> 00:12:04,420
the entire Mount Wangcheng was sealed off

262
00:12:04,580 --> 00:12:05,980
and no one was allowed to enter the mountain.

263
00:12:07,420 --> 00:12:08,460
But on that day,

264
00:12:08,980 --> 00:12:11,420
Lei Hong came and demanded a duel with you.

265
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:13,220
Our disciples couldn't stop him.

266
00:12:13,700 --> 00:12:15,100
Just as he was about to enter the mountain,

267
00:12:15,420 --> 00:12:16,980
Li Hanyi came.

268
00:12:23,420 --> 00:12:24,340
I was too ignorant.

269
00:12:24,820 --> 00:12:25,460
You should return.

270
00:12:26,380 --> 00:12:27,780
I will pay you a visit

271
00:12:28,260 --> 00:12:29,060
when you become a sword deity.

272
00:12:30,020 --> 00:12:31,100
However, you shall not

273
00:12:31,860 --> 00:12:32,660
enter Mount Wangcheng today.

274
00:12:34,260 --> 00:12:34,820
[Mount Wangcheng]

275
00:12:34,820 --> 00:12:35,540
[Mount Wangcheng]
Sword deity?

276
00:12:37,900 --> 00:12:39,180
I will definitely become a sword deity.

277
00:12:43,940 --> 00:12:47,380
[Gate of Mist]

278
00:12:49,060 --> 00:12:50,100
How is he doing?

279
00:12:51,980 --> 00:12:53,060
He has regained consciousness

280
00:12:53,380 --> 00:12:54,460
with the help of the celestial masters.

281
00:12:55,340 --> 00:12:57,380
However, it will take a long time

282
00:12:57,940 --> 00:12:59,300
for him to recover.

283
00:13:00,860 --> 00:13:01,500
Okay.

284
00:13:02,180 --> 00:13:03,140
Master Lyu,

285
00:13:03,660 --> 00:13:05,540
please tell him that I was here.

286
00:13:07,980 --> 00:13:09,100
You should know

287
00:13:09,260 --> 00:13:10,380
what happened next.

288
00:13:10,860 --> 00:13:13,300
In the end, you could not win against the heavens.

289
00:13:14,140 --> 00:13:15,660
Both you and Master Lyu were hurt.

290
00:13:16,020 --> 00:13:17,660
Master Lyu passed away not long after that.

291
00:13:17,820 --> 00:13:19,700
Since then, no one spoke about it.

292
00:13:20,180 --> 00:13:21,140
Why did no one speak about it?

293
00:13:21,780 --> 00:13:22,620
My sister is a prideful person.

294
00:13:22,860 --> 00:13:23,460
She couldn't bring him away

295
00:13:23,460 --> 00:13:24,300
after three visits.

296
00:13:24,780 --> 00:13:25,260
She might

297
00:13:25,260 --> 00:13:25,980
never come again.

298
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:27,340
Saint Zhao,

299
00:13:28,380 --> 00:13:30,100
we're heading to the hero banquet
held by the Lei Clan.

300
00:13:30,620 --> 00:13:31,260
Xueyue Sword Deity

301
00:13:31,260 --> 00:13:32,180
will join us.

302
00:13:32,740 --> 00:13:33,540
Will you join us?

303
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:35,260
And my master.

304
00:13:35,620 --> 00:13:36,460
He is Lei Hong.

305
00:13:36,820 --> 00:13:37,620
He's a member of the Lei Clan too.

306
00:13:38,980 --> 00:13:39,420
Kiddo,

307
00:13:40,220 --> 00:13:41,020
what will happen

308
00:13:41,580 --> 00:13:42,180
if I don't leave the mountain?

309
00:13:43,220 --> 00:13:44,340
My sister might meet my master.

310
00:13:44,820 --> 00:13:45,820
And my master might not

311
00:13:45,820 --> 00:13:46,500
let her leave him again.

312
00:13:47,100 --> 00:13:48,020
And what if I leave the mountain?

313
00:13:49,260 --> 00:13:50,340
Everything will be under your control.

314
00:13:53,580 --> 00:13:54,220
You're right.

315
00:13:55,140 --> 00:13:56,820
So, are you leaving the mountain or not?

316
00:14:04,180 --> 00:14:06,140
In the Peach Blossom Village,
there is a peach blossom hut.

317
00:14:07,340 --> 00:14:09,180
A peach blossom lover lives
in the peach blossom hut.

318
00:14:10,380 --> 00:14:12,620
From day to day half-drunk, half-sober he'd appear.

319
00:14:13,460 --> 00:14:16,180
The peach flowers
blossom and fall from year to year.

320
00:14:18,580 --> 00:14:19,260
You guys should leave.

321
00:14:24,180 --> 00:14:24,580
What...

322
00:14:25,580 --> 00:14:26,420
Let's go then.

323
00:14:32,580 --> 00:14:34,980
What's with him and his stupid poem?

324
00:14:35,620 --> 00:14:36,660
Will Zhao Yuzhen

325
00:14:36,940 --> 00:14:38,860
leave the mountain or not?

326
00:14:39,340 --> 00:14:40,180
No one can tell

327
00:14:40,500 --> 00:14:41,420
what is on my master's mind.

328
00:14:44,300 --> 00:14:46,020
Will a huge change occur

329
00:14:46,180 --> 00:14:48,260
if your master does leave the mountain?

330
00:14:50,220 --> 00:14:51,020
Master hasn't left

331
00:14:51,020 --> 00:14:51,900
the mountain before.

332
00:14:52,260 --> 00:14:53,140
So no one knows.

333
00:14:54,060 --> 00:14:55,140
Maybe

334
00:14:55,580 --> 00:14:57,100
my great master tricked him

335
00:14:57,500 --> 00:14:58,780
so that he would stay

336
00:14:58,780 --> 00:14:59,580
in Mount Wangcheng forever.

337
00:15:00,740 --> 00:15:02,380
Great Master isn't as dumb as you.

338
00:15:03,580 --> 00:15:05,140
Masters of the sect
have their lives determined by the heavens.

339
00:15:05,780 --> 00:15:07,020
What Great Master had said

340
00:15:07,020 --> 00:15:07,780
might be true.

341
00:15:09,420 --> 00:15:10,580
Determined by the heavens?

342
00:15:10,900 --> 00:15:11,660
Enough already.

343
00:15:12,700 --> 00:15:13,660
Whether Zhao Yuzhen comes or not

344
00:15:14,020 --> 00:15:14,820
depends on your sister

345
00:15:15,260 --> 00:15:16,210
and himself.

346
00:15:16,340 --> 00:15:17,500
It has nothing to do with you.

347
00:15:18,220 --> 00:15:19,300
You'd already said

348
00:15:19,300 --> 00:15:19,980
what you were supposed to say.

349
00:15:20,620 --> 00:15:21,580
We should leave now.

350
00:15:22,220 --> 00:15:23,540
No matter if it's Li Hanyi

351
00:15:23,540 --> 00:15:24,420
or Zhao Yuzhen,

352
00:15:25,140 --> 00:15:26,260
with their powers

353
00:15:26,260 --> 00:15:27,140
that can help them travel 1,000 li per day,

354
00:15:27,660 --> 00:15:28,580
heading to Lei Fortress

355
00:15:28,580 --> 00:15:29,740
is a piece of cake to them.

356
00:15:29,820 --> 00:15:30,620
But us?

357
00:15:31,020 --> 00:15:32,580
We'll be laughingstocks if we don't depart now.

358
00:15:33,740 --> 00:15:34,180
Let's go.

359
00:15:34,300 --> 00:15:35,220
You're right.

360
00:15:36,340 --> 00:15:37,340
I don't know anything

361
00:15:37,340 --> 00:15:37,940
about the heavens.

362
00:15:38,300 --> 00:15:38,980
I only believe in one thing.

363
00:15:39,380 --> 00:15:40,660
When there's a will, there's a way.

364
00:15:41,220 --> 00:15:41,780
Farewell.

365
00:15:42,460 --> 00:15:43,020
Farewell.

366
00:15:48,580 --> 00:15:49,660
I forgot to ask you something.

367
00:15:50,460 --> 00:15:51,500
How did you convince your sister

368
00:15:51,780 --> 00:15:52,740
to meet Lei Hong together with you?

369
00:15:53,340 --> 00:15:53,980
Judging from her personality,

370
00:15:53,980 --> 00:15:54,900
she'll never agree to it.

371
00:15:55,700 --> 00:15:57,620
Actually, I deceived Hanyi.

372
00:15:59,340 --> 00:16:00,380
You know how to deceive people?

373
00:16:00,980 --> 00:16:02,100
I lied to her

374
00:16:02,620 --> 00:16:03,860
and said that my master

375
00:16:03,980 --> 00:16:04,900
is terminally ill.

376
00:16:05,140 --> 00:16:06,300
I said he wants to see her

377
00:16:06,300 --> 00:16:07,100
and have no regrets

378
00:16:07,260 --> 00:16:08,180
before he dies.

379
00:16:08,700 --> 00:16:09,460
That's how Hanyi agreed to it.

380
00:16:10,380 --> 00:16:11,100
Does your master

381
00:16:11,100 --> 00:16:11,940
know that you jinxed him?

382
00:16:12,420 --> 00:16:13,500
He won't care about anything I say

383
00:16:13,540 --> 00:16:14,780
as long as he can see Hanyi.

384
00:16:17,060 --> 00:16:18,500
Lei Wujie, I didn't expect this from you.

385
00:16:18,900 --> 00:16:20,340
I guess you've turned cunning too.

386
00:16:21,140 --> 00:16:23,580
You flatter me. You're an expert yourself.

387
00:16:24,140 --> 00:16:25,060
Last question.

388
00:16:25,660 --> 00:16:27,220
Are you sure you know the way to Lei Fortress?

389
00:16:28,020 --> 00:16:28,580
Don't worry.

390
00:16:29,580 --> 00:16:30,580
I've lived in Lei Fortress

391
00:16:30,580 --> 00:16:31,300
for over a decade.

392
00:16:31,780 --> 00:16:32,660
I remember its scent.

393
00:16:33,180 --> 00:16:34,460
So I will never forget it.

394
00:16:36,140 --> 00:16:36,820
Follow me.

395
00:16:50,140 --> 00:16:51,740
You're heading the wrong way. Come back.

396
00:16:55,060 --> 00:16:55,460
Look for yourself.

397
00:16:56,740 --> 00:16:57,620
You're an idiot.

398
00:17:03,180 --> 00:17:04,660
That person isn't Xiao Chuhe.

399
00:17:06,420 --> 00:17:08,300
Xiao Chuhe has been nowhere to be found
for four years.

400
00:17:08,780 --> 00:17:09,860
If he appears again,

401
00:17:10,340 --> 00:17:12,140
he'll definitely be different.

402
00:17:14,260 --> 00:17:15,100
Have you seen him before?

403
00:17:15,780 --> 00:17:16,740
I once saw him from a long distance

404
00:17:16,740 --> 00:17:17,860
when I was in Tianqi City.

405
00:17:18,700 --> 00:17:20,100
Back then, I received an order

406
00:17:20,100 --> 00:17:21,100
to kill him.

407
00:17:21,900 --> 00:17:23,420
However, someone acted first.

408
00:17:24,220 --> 00:17:24,940
I thought he was dead

409
00:17:25,580 --> 00:17:26,940
all these years.

410
00:17:28,300 --> 00:17:29,900
Does the Leader know about this?

411
00:17:31,500 --> 00:17:32,610
It doesn't matter

412
00:17:32,610 --> 00:17:33,380
if the Leader knows about this.

413
00:17:34,100 --> 00:17:35,460
It doesn't matter if that Xiao Chuhe

414
00:17:35,460 --> 00:17:36,340
is the real deal or not.

415
00:17:37,420 --> 00:17:39,940
Dark River just needs an opportunity

416
00:17:40,500 --> 00:17:41,900
to set foot in Tianqi City.

417
00:17:43,340 --> 00:17:43,940
You're right.

418
00:17:44,980 --> 00:17:45,940
We've been living in darkness

419
00:17:45,940 --> 00:17:47,100
for too long.

420
00:17:47,780 --> 00:17:48,580
Are you going

421
00:17:48,580 --> 00:17:49,660
to kill those two youngsters?

422
00:17:50,420 --> 00:17:51,340
It's a waste

423
00:17:51,860 --> 00:17:53,020
of your talent.

424
00:17:53,740 --> 00:17:54,620
I will head southward

425
00:17:54,620 --> 00:17:55,500
to stop someone.

426
00:17:56,100 --> 00:17:57,700
It seems like that person

427
00:17:57,700 --> 00:17:58,580
is heading to Lei Clan too.

428
00:17:58,940 --> 00:17:59,940
She's a variable

429
00:18:00,140 --> 00:18:00,860
in this operation.

430
00:18:01,260 --> 00:18:02,060
What kind of person is she

431
00:18:02,420 --> 00:18:04,140
for you to be so cautious?

432
00:18:04,420 --> 00:18:06,740
It's Li Hanyi, the Xueyue Sword Deity.

433
00:18:08,420 --> 00:18:09,140
Who are you guys?

434
00:18:09,860 --> 00:18:10,460
Why are you

435
00:18:10,460 --> 00:18:11,140
blocking our path?

436
00:18:12,060 --> 00:18:12,780
Lei Wujie,

437
00:18:13,340 --> 00:18:14,180
these people are different

438
00:18:14,180 --> 00:18:15,020
from the ones we used to see.

439
00:18:15,740 --> 00:18:16,740
You need to understand something.

440
00:18:17,540 --> 00:18:19,100
They're here to take lives.

441
00:18:20,020 --> 00:18:21,060
Who exactly are they?

442
00:18:22,060 --> 00:18:22,780
Dark River.

443
00:18:23,540 --> 00:18:24,420
Dark River?

444
00:18:25,660 --> 00:18:27,140
Do you mean the assassin syndicate

445
00:18:27,300 --> 00:18:29,060
that's occupied the top eight slots
of the League of Assassins?

446
00:18:29,300 --> 00:18:31,020
That's right, my surname is Su.

447
00:18:31,860 --> 00:18:34,020
[Su Changli, Dark River]
I'm Su Changli of the Su family.

448
00:18:34,260 --> 00:18:35,420
It's my first time seeing assassins

449
00:18:35,420 --> 00:18:36,500
who tell us about their names.

450
00:18:36,820 --> 00:18:37,820
I told you guys my name

451
00:18:38,420 --> 00:18:39,300
because you guys

452
00:18:39,300 --> 00:18:39,980
will die soon.

453
00:18:51,740 --> 00:18:54,740
(Su Changli. He's an expert with big swords.)

454
00:18:55,180 --> 00:18:56,220
(He has a dominant aura.)

455
00:18:56,780 --> 00:18:58,860
(Seems like he's the leader of the bunch.)

456
00:19:00,940 --> 00:19:01,460
Xiao Se,

457
00:19:01,900 --> 00:19:02,820
this is interesting.

458
00:19:03,820 --> 00:19:04,980
The first opponents

459
00:19:04,980 --> 00:19:05,700
we met on our adventure

460
00:19:06,180 --> 00:19:06,860
were assassins too.

461
00:19:08,100 --> 00:19:08,580
But this time,

462
00:19:08,580 --> 00:19:09,420
Lian isn't around.

463
00:19:10,300 --> 00:19:11,420
We can only depend on ourselves.

464
00:19:12,180 --> 00:19:12,860
You're wrong.

465
00:19:14,380 --> 00:19:15,100
We can only depend on you.

466
00:19:17,660 --> 00:19:18,340
Xiao Se!

467
00:19:23,980 --> 00:19:24,500
(Master,)

468
00:19:25,060 --> 00:19:26,140
is there anything I should take note of

469
00:19:26,500 --> 00:19:27,380
when I go on adventures in the future?

470
00:19:27,860 --> 00:19:29,700
Just remember this.

471
00:19:30,300 --> 00:19:32,740
Speed is of the essence.

472
00:19:42,820 --> 00:19:44,300
(What if speed doesn't help)

473
00:19:44,300 --> 00:19:44,900
in contesting against my opponents?

474
00:19:45,260 --> 00:19:46,740
Just remember this then.

475
00:19:47,140 --> 00:19:49,180
Run if you can't win.

476
00:19:49,860 --> 00:19:50,860
Master,

477
00:19:50,860 --> 00:19:51,900
you have great foresight indeed.

478
00:19:53,540 --> 00:19:54,580
However, even if Walking on Clouds

479
00:19:54,580 --> 00:19:55,300
doesn't consume any inner force,

480
00:19:56,260 --> 00:19:57,540
it's extremely exhausting.

481
00:19:58,740 --> 00:19:59,780
I'm in trouble.

482
00:20:01,540 --> 00:20:02,300
(Initially, I wanted)

483
00:20:02,300 --> 00:20:03,220
(to distract some of them)

484
00:20:03,700 --> 00:20:04,460
(so that I could meet up)

485
00:20:04,500 --> 00:20:05,620
(with Lei Wujie after he defeated them.)

486
00:20:06,540 --> 00:20:07,700
(But judging from the situation,)

487
00:20:08,060 --> 00:20:09,020
(I think I can no longer run.)

488
00:20:09,940 --> 00:20:10,980
(And Lei Wujie)

489
00:20:10,980 --> 00:20:11,860
(can't seem to get rid of them either.)

490
00:20:34,220 --> 00:20:34,980
Only I can

491
00:20:35,460 --> 00:20:36,260
go after a scoundrel like Xiao Se.

492
00:20:36,700 --> 00:20:37,500
You guys have no right.

493
00:20:40,140 --> 00:20:41,020
Beware of them.

494
00:20:42,500 --> 00:20:43,460
I know

495
00:20:43,460 --> 00:20:44,140
you cannot defeat these bandits.

496
00:20:44,980 --> 00:20:46,260
But I'm not as weak as you.

497
00:21:20,820 --> 00:21:21,460
Are you okay?

498
00:21:22,260 --> 00:21:23,060
That was dangerous,

499
00:21:23,060 --> 00:21:23,820
you know?

500
00:21:24,220 --> 00:21:25,100
Aren't you afraid that you'll hit me by accident?

501
00:21:25,700 --> 00:21:26,740
I'm not one of the Tang family.

502
00:21:27,340 --> 00:21:28,180
I have no choice but to try my luck.

503
00:21:28,700 --> 00:21:29,580
Why do you have Lian's weapon

504
00:21:29,580 --> 00:21:30,340
with you?

505
00:21:31,020 --> 00:21:31,980
He lost them to me after a drinking game.

506
00:21:32,500 --> 00:21:33,100
Enough.

507
00:21:33,580 --> 00:21:34,420
Let's hurry and find

508
00:21:34,420 --> 00:21:35,060
Lei Wujie.

509
00:21:35,660 --> 00:21:36,620
He might be in danger.

510
00:21:37,180 --> 00:21:38,380
That guy called Su Changli,

511
00:21:39,180 --> 00:21:40,420
I'm afraid I've underestimated him.

512
00:21:44,500 --> 00:21:45,020
Not bad at all.

513
00:21:45,300 --> 00:21:46,820
You've survived long enough under my sword.

514
00:21:47,220 --> 00:21:48,140
You can be proud of yourself.

515
00:21:48,540 --> 00:21:49,460
I'm not done yet.

516
00:21:50,300 --> 00:21:51,460
Although you're no match for me,

517
00:21:51,940 --> 00:21:53,180
you had a chance to escape.

518
00:21:53,620 --> 00:21:54,740
Why do you have to go all out to fight me?

519
00:21:55,460 --> 00:21:56,180
What if you go after my friends

520
00:21:56,580 --> 00:21:57,700
after I leave?

521
00:21:58,460 --> 00:21:59,980
Great. You're a loyal person.

522
00:22:00,340 --> 00:22:01,260
What a great man.

523
00:22:01,580 --> 00:22:03,580
It's worth cutting your head off.

524
00:22:07,780 --> 00:22:08,420
Qianluo.

525
00:22:09,220 --> 00:22:10,180
Xiao Se, are you okay?

526
00:22:11,100 --> 00:22:11,740
Those assassins

527
00:22:11,980 --> 00:22:13,060
can't do anything to me.

528
00:22:13,820 --> 00:22:14,820
You guys would've been dead

529
00:22:15,220 --> 00:22:16,260
if I hadn't come here in time.

530
00:22:16,980 --> 00:22:17,860
Cut the crap.

531
00:22:31,980 --> 00:22:32,540
Let's take a break.

532
00:22:32,980 --> 00:22:34,020
Let's take a break.

533
00:22:35,700 --> 00:22:36,500
We almost died

534
00:22:36,500 --> 00:22:37,300
just now.

535
00:22:37,500 --> 00:22:38,100
That's right.

536
00:22:39,460 --> 00:22:40,380
I thought Second Master

537
00:22:40,380 --> 00:22:40,900
was guarding over you two?

538
00:22:41,500 --> 00:22:42,540
You have to ask this idiot

539
00:22:43,060 --> 00:22:43,820
why he took a huge detour

540
00:22:43,820 --> 00:22:44,620
and went

541
00:22:44,940 --> 00:22:46,060
to Mount Wangcheng.

542
00:22:46,540 --> 00:22:47,140
Qianluo,

543
00:22:47,420 --> 00:22:48,580
how did you find us?

544
00:22:49,420 --> 00:22:51,220
(I can't just tell them
that I've been following them)

545
00:22:51,260 --> 00:22:52,220
(right after they left the city.)

546
00:22:53,380 --> 00:22:54,220
I'll complain about you two

547
00:22:54,500 --> 00:22:55,220
to Second Master.

548
00:22:55,540 --> 00:22:56,380
She'll teach you guys a lesson.

549
00:22:57,220 --> 00:22:57,860
Let's go.

550
00:22:59,460 --> 00:23:00,220
Qianluo.

551
00:23:18,420 --> 00:23:19,900
Li Hanyi of Xueyue City.

552
00:23:20,860 --> 00:23:21,900
Su Muyu of Dark River.

553
00:23:23,180 --> 00:23:24,620
Do you remember that we once joined hands

554
00:23:25,740 --> 00:23:26,700
to fight against someone

555
00:23:27,540 --> 00:23:28,500
many years ago?

556
00:23:28,860 --> 00:23:29,820
I still remember the scene

557
00:23:30,420 --> 00:23:31,540
as if it was yesterday.

558
00:23:32,500 --> 00:23:33,740
But it looks like

559
00:23:34,620 --> 00:23:35,540
you're trying to kill me today.

560
00:23:37,740 --> 00:23:38,700
You cannot kill me

561
00:23:39,620 --> 00:23:40,580
by yourself.

562
00:23:42,020 --> 00:23:42,700
I'm afraid no one

563
00:23:43,180 --> 00:23:44,380
in this world

564
00:23:44,380 --> 00:23:45,900
can kill the Xueyue Sword Deity.

565
00:23:47,540 --> 00:23:48,780
What if I interfere?

566
00:23:51,380 --> 00:23:53,380
So, the two family heads of Dark River
are joining hands?

