00:34:16,660 --> 00:34:17,820
It's because you're Tang Lianyue,

847
00:34:17,820 --> 00:34:18,500
the best in Tang Clan.

848
00:34:19,180 --> 00:34:20,340
However, you cannot leave here alive.

849
00:34:21,340 --> 00:34:22,220
We

850
00:34:22,220 --> 00:34:22,980
will keep you here

851
00:34:23,620 --> 00:34:24,780
even if it means

852
00:34:24,780 --> 00:34:25,780
we and our brothers out there

853
00:34:26,500 --> 00:34:27,900
will die today.

854
00:34:29,700 --> 00:34:30,540
I don't intend to leave.

855
00:34:31,620 --> 00:34:32,460
However, you need to

856
00:34:32,980 --> 00:34:34,020
