884
00:35:39,740 --> 00:35:40,420
You do sound

885
00:35:40,420 --> 00:35:41,820
a little like Xiao Se now.

886
00:35:46,740 --> 00:35:47,340
Xiao Se,

887
00:35:47,740 --> 00:35:48,500
I think the noodles you make

888
00:35:48,500 --> 00:35:49,700
in Snowfall Villa taste better.

889
00:35:50,100 --> 00:35:51,100
Of course.

890
00:35:51,820 --> 00:35:53,780
The cooks I hire are the best

891
00:35:53,780 --> 00:35:55,380
within a 100-li radius.

892
00:35:55,660 --> 00:35:56,540
You're bragging again.

893
00:35:57,820 --> 00:35:58,580
I'm not.

894
00:35:59,180 --> 00:36:00,060
I ride the best horses,

895
00:36:00,340 --> 00:36:01,180
wear the best apparel,

896
00:36:01,740 --> 00:36:02,420
and have

897
00:36:02,820 --> 00:36:03,980
the most loyal friends.

898
00:36:06,500 --> 00:36:07,420
Qianluo,

899
00:36:08,420 --> 00:36:09,620
