903
00:36:19,620 --> 00:36:20,500
It's my first time

904
00:36:20,980 --> 00:36:22,300
hearing you calling me

905
00:36:22,300 --> 00:36:23,060
as your friend.

906
00:36:25,220 --> 00:36:27,700
If so, what did he call you before this?

907
00:36:28,860 --> 00:36:30,180
Fool.

908
00:36:30,620 --> 00:36:32,180
No, he calls me an airhead.

909
00:36:35,620 --> 00:36:36,220
Am I

910
00:36:36,220 --> 00:36:37,100
that rude?

911
00:36:38,020 --> 00:36:40,340
Besides, I'm your friend.

912
00:36:40,740 --> 00:36:41,660
But you owe me money.

913
00:36:41,940 --> 00:36:43,300
These are two different things.

914
00:36:43,380 --> 00:36:43,940
If so...

915
00:36:44,620 --> 00:36:46,540
If so, your bowl of noodles costs me 500 taels.

916
00:36:46,980 --> 00:36:47,580
And you've eaten it.

917
00:36:48,020 --> 00:36:50,180
Fine. 500 taels it is then.

918
00:36:50,660 --> 00:36:51,860
It's not like I can't afford it.

919
00:36:52,740 --> 00:36:53,740
I'll take it

920
00:36:53,740 --> 00:36:55,260
as repayment for saving me on Mount Wangcheng.

921
00:36:56,180 --> 00:36:57,540
If you had abandoned me back then,

922
00:36:58,100 --> 00:36:58,860
I would've been killed

923
00:36:59,300 --> 00:37:00,300
by Su Changli.

924
00:37:01,420 --> 00:37:02,140
If so, you should stop eating.

925
00:37:03,540 --> 00:37:04,340
What are you doing?

926
00:37:04,900 --> 00:37:05,700
I saved you

927
00:37:05,700 --> 00:37:06,340
because you're my friend.

928
00:37:07,220 --> 00:37:08,660
Xiao Se, even if you're a penniless fool

929
00:37:08,660 --> 00:37:09,820
that entertains people for a living,

930
00:37:10,220 --> 00:37:11,180
I will always save you

931
00:37:11,180 --> 00:37:11,900
as long as you're my friend.

932
00:37:12,820 --> 00:37:14,020
But you're viewing our friendship
in terms of silver taels.

933
00:37:14,380 --> 00:37:15,260
Forget about 500 taels.

934
00:37:15,580 --> 00:37:16,660
I won't take it even if you offer me 50,000 taels.

935
00:37:17,460 --> 00:37:18,700
So, are you saying

936
00:37:19,860 --> 00:37:21,420
that you're willing to risk your life

937
00:37:21,820 --> 00:37:22,620
for a friend like me?

938
00:37:23,660 --> 00:37:24,660
What will you do for a promise then?

939
00:37:25,220 --> 00:37:27,220
For example, you once told me

940
00:37:27,260 --> 00:37:29,060
that you promised your mother
that you would protect a certain person.

941
00:37:29,980 --> 00:37:30,940
One of them is concerned with loyalty,

942
00:37:30,940 --> 00:37:31,740
while the other is responsibility.

943
00:37:32,090 --> 00:37:32,940
What's the difference?

944
00:37:33,580 --> 00:37:34,220
Loyalty

945
00:37:34,460 --> 00:37:35,820
is the thing I treasure the most

946
00:37:35,820 --> 00:37:36,740
in my adventure as a martial artist.

947
00:37:37,020 --> 00:37:37,860
I can live for it

948
00:37:37,900 --> 00:37:38,780
and die for it.

949
00:37:39,540 --> 00:37:40,700
That responsibility is something

950
00:37:40,700 --> 00:37:41,340
I have to bear when I was born.

951
00:37:41,900 --> 00:37:43,220
It's a promise that I have to keep.

952
00:37:43,740 --> 00:37:45,140
But what if the person you need to protect

953
00:37:46,740 --> 00:37:48,100
is out to take my life?

954
00:37:48,580 --> 00:37:49,340
What will you do then?

955
00:37:54,220 --> 00:37:54,820
If so...

956
00:37:55,700 --> 00:37:56,700
If so, that means my mother

957
00:37:56,700 --> 00:37:57,300
is doing the wrong thing.

958
00:37:57,460 --> 00:37:58,460
That means that person is not worth protecting.

959
00:37:58,700 --> 00:37:59,740
I'll escape together with you.

960
00:38:03,700 --> 00:38:04,420
If so, what if

961
00:38:05,940 --> 00:38:07,900
the person you need to protect is...

962
00:38:12,820 --> 00:38:13,660
Lei,

963
00:38:14,660 --> 00:38:15,420
why are you tearing up

964
00:38:15,420 --> 00:38:16,740
at his words?

965
00:38:17,900 --> 00:38:19,260
I'm not tearing up.

966
00:38:24,700 --> 00:38:25,260
What's the matter?

967
00:38:27,540 --> 00:38:28,540
It's Drunken Touch.

968
00:38:29,140 --> 00:38:30,020
You do know your thing.

969
00:38:43,260 --> 00:38:44,060
What's going on?

970
00:38:45,300 --> 00:38:45,900
Xiao Se,

971
00:38:46,380 --> 00:38:47,100
we're poisoned.

972
00:38:51,980 --> 00:38:52,540
Take this.

973
00:38:59,020 --> 00:39:00,300
An expert in Water Coagulation Technique

974
00:39:00,700 --> 00:39:02,700
who can use Drunken Touch at the same time?

975
00:39:04,300 --> 00:39:05,820
You must be a member of Dark River's Mu family.

976
00:39:07,540 --> 00:39:08,700
I'm Mu Ying

977
00:39:09,900 --> 00:39:10,700
