of the Mu family.

978
00:39:15,980 --> 00:39:16,940
You guys

979
00:39:17,300 --> 00:39:18,580
are relentless.

980
00:39:19,420 --> 00:39:20,500
I assume you just took

981
00:39:20,500 --> 00:39:21,380
Penglai Pill.

982
00:39:22,540 --> 00:39:24,780
That medicine can neutralize

983
00:39:24,780 --> 00:39:25,700
my Drunken Touch.

984
00:39:26,300 --> 00:39:27,740
