985
00:39:28,180 --> 00:39:29,220
It's too late for them

986
00:39:30,100 --> 00:39:31,460
to take the medicine.

987
00:39:32,410 --> 00:39:33,340
Shut up!

988
00:39:37,380 --> 00:39:39,140
So, this is the legendary
Stillwater Sword Technique

989
00:39:39,140 --> 00:39:40,340
of Xueyue Sword Deity?

990
00:39:53,060 --> 00:39:53,940
I can't use my inner force.

991
00:39:54,500 --> 00:39:55,100
Lei Wujie,

992
00:39:55,460 --> 00:39:55,980
Qianluo,

993
00:39:56,940 --> 00:39:57,980
don't use your zhenqi recklessly.

994
00:39:59,220 --> 00:40:00,620
Surrender yourselves,

995
00:40:01,020 --> 00:40:01,940
and you guys can die

996
00:40:01,940 --> 00:40:02,900
