997
00:40:03,980 --> 00:40:05,180
Seems like you're getting ahead of yourself.

998
00:40:06,300 --> 00:40:07,020
Don't forget.

999
00:40:07,900 --> 00:40:09,420
I'm not affected by your Drunken Touch.

1000
00:40:11,500 --> 00:40:13,340
You're not a martial artist.

1001
00:40:14,540 --> 00:40:15,140
Xiao Se,

1002
00:40:15,580 --> 00:40:16,780
Lei Wujie and I will stall him.

1003
00:40:17,100 --> 00:40:17,820
You should run.

1004
00:40:20,660 --> 00:40:21,820
Your friends

1005
00:40:22,340 --> 00:40:23,780
are going to die

1006
00:40:24,220 --> 00:40:25,940
if they use their zhenqi recklessly.

1007
00:40:26,180 --> 00:40:26,820
Shut up.

1008
00:40:30,020 --> 00:40:30,660
Mu Ying,

1009
00:40:31,620 --> 00:40:32,900
