1028
00:41:08,380 --> 00:41:09,620
We need to end this quickly.

1029
00:41:10,700 --> 00:41:12,660
Do you have any news about Xiao Se and his gang?

1030
00:41:13,060 --> 00:41:14,020
I don't.

1031
00:41:14,540 --> 00:41:15,820
Didn't the Lei family write to us?

1032
00:41:16,100 --> 00:41:16,620
No.

1033
00:41:17,020 --> 00:41:18,100
I heard from Tang

1034
00:41:18,300 --> 00:41:18,980
